HEADWORD: Autogamy
<hw>Au*tog"a*my</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Auto-</ets> + Gr. <?/ marriage.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Self-fertilization, the fertilizing pollen being derived from the
same blossom as the pistil acted upon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autogeneal</ent>⟦br⟧
